@enemies_done

Our editorial line is set. The Vorwärts will focus its fire on the [+ enemy_1 +][? if enemy_2 != 0: , with secondary attention to the [+ enemy_2 +][? if enemy_3 != 0: and passing criticism of the [+ enemy_3 +] ?] ?].

[? if enemy_1 = "KPD" and enemy_2 = "NSDAP" or enemy_1 = "NSDAP" and enemy_2 = "KPD": Targeting both extremes simultaneously signals republican commitment — though some on our left see this as a false equivalence. ?]
[? if enemy_1 = "NSDAP" and enemy_2 = "DNVP" or enemy_1 = "DNVP" and enemy_2 = "NSDAP": Attacking both wings of the nationalist right may help consolidate our anti-fascist credentials. ?]
[? if enemy_1 = "KPD" and ideology = "reformist": Our reformist course and anti-Communist line are now fully aligned. The bourgeois press will take note. ?]
